text: Duke Moore, (July 15, 1913 as James Moore â€“ November 16, 1976), was an American actor. He appeared only in movies made by Ed Wood. Between 1953 and 1970, Moore appeared in the following Wood movies: Crossroads of Laredo; Final Curtain; Night of the Ghouls; Plan 9 from Outer Space; The Sinister Urge, and Take it Out in Trade.
